Package: sustainableNutRients
Type: Package
Title: Map foods to Matvaretabellen food composition and SHARP ID environmental impact databases
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Aslaug Angelsen
Maintainer: Aslaug Angelsen <aslaug.angelsen@gmail.com>
Description: Standardise food names in recipes or food diaries and map them to
    the Norwegian food composition datatable Matvaretabellen and the environmental
    impact database SHARP Indicator Database to calculate nutrient content and
    environmental impact.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports:
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    rlang,
    stringi,
    stringr,
    tibble,
    tidyr,
    tidyselect
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
